'''Freeze boots''' were used by the [[Megonite moss/Legends|megonite]] miners on [[Phelarion/Legends|Phelarion]]. Freeze boots were equipped with technology that would instantly freeze the megonite in order to prevent it from overheating and exploding when stepped on.

